base: Try different directories when searching for a ref
from: https://www.leshenko.net/p/ugit/#search-ref-directories

from:Nikita
allow different ref_path to be written
ways:
  1:Root (.ugit): This way we can specify refs/tags/mytag
  2:.ugit/refs: This way we can specify tags/mytag
  3:.ugit/refs/tags: This way we can specify mytag
  4:.ugit/refs/heads: This will be needed for a future change



